51:12.433 --> 51:13.766
What is it?

51:13.766 --> 51:19.266
♪ ♪

51:29.800 --> 51:30.800
Clara?

51:30.800 --> 51:36.300
♪ ♪

51:36.300 --> 51:38.666
I thought I'd made it
perfectly clear that you were

51:38.666 --> 51:41.466
never to darken my doors again!

51:41.466 --> 51:42.533
Throw her out!
No!

51:42.533 --> 51:44.566
Aunt...

51:44.566 --> 51:47.100
I have nowhere else to turn.

51:47.100 --> 51:48.933
I have been used
and abandoned.

51:48.933 --> 51:50.500
That is no concern
of ours.

51:50.500 --> 51:52.833
Please!

51:52.833 --> 51:54.533
I am with child!

51:54.533 --> 51:56.033
Oh!

51:57.233 --> 51:59.366
It is Edward's!

51:59.366 --> 52:03.566
♪ ♪

52:05.700 --> 52:06.833
