52:16.433 --> 52:17.500
♪ ♪

52:17.500 --> 52:18.466
ALISON:
So, who are you dreaming of?

52:18.466 --> 52:20.400
Your strange new employer?

52:20.400 --> 52:21.433
Or a certain colonel?

52:21.433 --> 52:23.033
(sighing):
Alison.

52:23.033 --> 52:24.133
GEORGIANA:
What do you want from me?

52:24.133 --> 52:25.866
Isn't it obvious?

52:25.866 --> 52:27.866
ALISON:
He's both a hero and a poet.

52:27.866 --> 52:29.000
LENNOX:
Be on your guard

52:29.000 --> 52:30.033
